                    </div>
                    <span>A highly rewarding read is what this book offers. One of the reasons I enjoy reading of another's life is to see the twists and turns that occur in the course of events. Most of the time (never always) the route is circuitous before a life's occupation is finally realized. In this case Pete Hamill is talented from childhood due to a creative brain and the ability to draw. This lead to many many adventures and the final destination of author. What a trip! Everything is well written and his amours are something to behold. I coudl not put this book down and read it quickly.</span>
                  
              
